# Laravel Complete Feature Generator

**Command**: `/laravel:feature [name] [options]`

**Description**: Generates a complete Laravel feature with model, migration, controller, requests, tests, and views/components based on project type.

## Usage

```bash
/laravel:feature User --api
/laravel:feature BlogPost --with-policy
/laravel:feature Product --fields="name:string,price:decimal,description:text"
/laravel:feature Order --relationships="belongsTo:User,hasMany:OrderItem"
```

## Options

- `--api` - Generate API-only resources (no views)
- `--with-policy` - Include authorization policy
- `--with-observer` - Include model observer
- `--fields="field:type,..."` - Define model fields
- `--relationships="type:Model,..."` - Define model relationships
- `--soft-deletes` - Add soft deletes to model
- `--timestamps=false` - Disable timestamps
- `--resource` - Generate API resource class
- `--collection` - Generate API resource collection

## Generated Files

### Core Files (Always Generated)
- `app/Models/{Name}.php` - Eloquent model
- `database/migrations/{timestamp}_create_{table}_table.php` - Database migration
- `app/Http/Controllers/{Name}Controller.php` - Resource controller
- `app/Http/Requests/Store{Name}Request.php` - Store validation
- `app/Http/Requests/Update{Name}Request.php` - Update validation
- `tests/Feature/{Name}ControllerTest.php` - Feature tests
- `tests/Unit/{Name}Test.php` - Unit tests
- `database/factories/{Name}Factory.php` - Model factory

### Conditional Files (Based on Project Type)
- `app/Http/Resources/{Name}Resource.php` - API resource (if --api or API project)
- `app/Http/Resources/{Name}Collection.php` - API collection (if --collection)
- `app/Policies/{Name}Policy.php` - Authorization policy (if --with-policy)
- `app/Observers/{Name}Observer.php` - Model observer (if --with-observer)

### Frontend Files (Based on Detected Stack)
- **Blade**: `resources/views/{name}/index.blade.php`, `create.blade.php`, `show.blade.php`, `edit.blade.php`
- **Livewire**: `app/Http/Livewire/{Name}Index.php`, `{Name}Create.php`, `{Name}Edit.php` + views
- **Inertia**: `resources/js/Pages/{Name}/Index.vue`, `Create.vue`, `Show.vue`, `Edit.vue`

## Implementation

This command intelligently generates a complete feature based on your project's detected configuration:

### Step 1: Analyze Requirements
```javascript
