// Feature tests covering all endpoints
// Unit tests for model relationships and business logic
// Factory with realistic fake data
```

### Step 5: Generate Frontend (Based on Stack)
```php
// Detect project type and generate appropriate frontend files
// Blade views, Livewire components, or Inertia pages
// Include proper form handling and validation display
```

### Step 6: Update Routes
```php
// Add resource routes to appropriate route file
